The verification runs for this model follow this architecture:


SIM_01a_table_lookup_set_nominal
  This is the main sim, testing the operation of the following classes
  under a typical configuration:
     table-lookup-set (and thereby the table-manager)
     generic-multi-input-table
     table-independent-variable

SIM_01b_table_lookup_set_faults
  This sim tests whether misconfigurations are correctly caught; it continues
  the testing of the same classes from SIM_01a_table_lookup_set_nominal.

SIM_02_simple_table_lookup
  This sim tests the specifics of the simple-table-lookup manager
  (SimpleTableLookup).
  It includes verification of nominal operations and catching of
  configuration errors.

SIM_03_simple_table_lookup_for_angles
  This sim tests the operation of the SingleInputTableForAngles class, using
  the simple-table-lookup manager.
  It includes verification of nominal operations and catching of
  configuration errors.

SIM_04_table_lookup_for_quaternions
  Tests the operation of the SingleInputTableForQuaternions class, using the
  generic table-lookup-set manager.
  It includes verification of nominal operations and catching of
  configuration errors.

SIM_05_independent_wraparound
  Test the operation of the TableIndependentVariable_WrapAround, using the
  generic table-lookup-set manager.
  It includes verification of nominal operations and catching of
  configuration errors.

SIM_06_transpose_data_manager
  Tests the operation of the TableManagerTransposeDataSet table-manager.
  It includes verification of nominal operations and catching of
  configuration errors.

SIM_10_special_cases
  Tests special cases not uniquely coverable by previous sims.
